headline: AvalonBay Communities, Inc. Announces Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Release Date
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., January 09, 2025--AVALONBAY COMMUNITIES, INC. (NYSE: AVB) (the "Company") will release its fourth quarter 2024 earnings on February 5, 2025 after the market close. The Company will hold a conference call on February 6, 2025 at 1:00 PM Eastern Time (ET) to discuss its fourth quarter 2024 results.
